itting structure is reduced in size. Dense gas mass\nestimates for high redshift galaxies may need to be corrected for this effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 20 Jun 2018 20:26:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-08"}
