ificantly higher than predictions from semi-analytic models\nfor the progenitor of this supernova.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jun 2018 05:38:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 24 Sep 2018 08:19:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-10-17"}
