e findings,\nwe suggest Stack Overflow raise awareness of their users, both answerers and\nvisitors, to the problem of outdated and license-violating code snippets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jun 2018 09:59:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-22"}
